export default function Lessons() { return (

In 9 Lessons we will look at the Book of Revelation divided into 22 (A-V) parts.

Lesson #1 [1]:

(A) Introduction

(B) Christ and the 7 Golden Candlesticks

Lesson #2 [2-3]:

(C) 7 Letters to 7 Churches

Lesson #3 [4-5]:

(D) Vision of the Throne

(E) Who is Worthy to Open Book of Seven Seals?

Lesson #4 [6-8:1]:

(F) Opening of the 7 Seals

(G) 144,000

Lesson #5 [8:2-13; 9-11]:

(I) 7 Angels and 7 Trumpets

(J) Measure the Temple of God

(K) 2 Witnesses

Lesson #6 [12-13]:

(L) Sun-clothed Woman

(M) 2 Beasts and the Dragon

Lesson #7 [14-18]:

(N) A Lamb Stood on Mount Sion

(O) Judgement Hour Messages

(P) 7 Last Plagues in Vials

(Q) Fall of Babylon

Lesson #8 [19-20]:

(R) The Marriage and Marriage Feast of the Lamb

(S) Millenial Kingdom

(T) Last Judgment

Lesson #9 [21-22]:

(U) All Things New

(V) Closing

) }
